<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>Bishopsgate Street Without,</placeName>
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><placeName><settlement><seg rend="large">L</seg>ondon</settlement>, <hi rend="small">E.C.</hi></placeName> <date when="1882-05-03"><seg rend="italic black" n="date liv_020085_0001">May 3<hi rend="sup underline">rd</hi></seg> 18<seg rend="italic black" n="date liv_020085_0001">82</seg></date></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>F.W. Chesson Esq.</persName>
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/><placeName>17 King Wm. St.</placeName>
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="words"/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><settlement>Strand</settlement> <hi rend="small">W.C.</hi></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Dear Sir,</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="words"/>I called to see you
<lb/><date when="1882-05-02">yesterday</date> morning but learned
<lb/>that you do not arrive until
<lb/>12 O clock. <space extent="1" unit="chars"/>Will you be
<lb/>Kind enough to grant me the
<lb/>loan of &#xa3;2 as it is now
<lb/><del><gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="illegible"/></del><add place="over-text">very</add> close upon a year since
<lb/>I obtained that contribution from

	<pb facs="liv_020085_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>you. If you will grant my
<lb/>much needed request I
<lb/>will promise faithfully not to
<lb/>molest you again; at least for
<lb/>the space of a year. Please
<lb/>be good Enough to oblige me as
<lb/>I can assure you I must
<lb/>make up <del>a bit</del> &#xa3;5 by <date when="1882-05-03">Saturday</date>
<lb/>if possible or I may get into
<lb/> trouble. <space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I will return it at
<lb/>the Earliest possible moment.</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>Trusting to hear from you
<lb/>soon,</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I am
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><space extent="4" unit="chars"/>Yr obt. servant
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="words"/><persName>W.I. Craft.</persName>
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="words"/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><seg n="container liv_020085_0002"><seg n="horizontal-circle liv_020085_0002">âˆž</seg></seg></p>


